Description: Inspired by a group of extraordinary Irishmen who led lives of great adventure, this is a pub of epic proportions that was built in Ireland and shipped to the heart of Las Vegas! As for food and drink, our signature dishes are made of only the freshest, natural Irish ingredients that pair perfectly with the finest stouts, ales, lagers, and spirits.
Location: 3790 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: A culinary journey of American style food, wine and beerGo on a culinary journey with food, wine and beer from coast to coast, all in one American setting. America also features a massive 90 x 20 foot map of the United States, highlighting America_s most iconic landmarks.America DonutsIt doesn't get more American than a delicious good old fashioned donut with a fresh cup of coffee. Baked fresh daily, the donuts, pastries and desserts at America Donuts will send your taste buds on a journey of deliciousness.
Location: 3790 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Get your slice on at New York Pizzeria!At NYP, the slices are cut big from each and every 18" gourmet signature pizza oven-baked to perfection. From slices or full pies loaded with toppings, to calzones, Stromboli, garlic knots, and salads, NYP has something for every appetite - big or small and uses only fresh top-quality ingredients in their made-from-scratch recipes. For the ultimate pizza and beer lover's experience, enjoy several NYP menu selections accompanying the rich hand-crafted malt brews at Pour 24_.
Location: 3791 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Now that's Italian - New York-styleTravel to romantic Italy and indulge in housemade and imported pasta; wood-fired pizza, rotisserie chicken and duck; hearty steaks and chops; mesquite grilled fish; and the season's picks for salads and soups at our purveyor of award-winning Italian cuisine: Il Fornaio. Complete this Old World culinary getaway with a delightful dessert and robust Italian coffee.
Location: 3792 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Healthy, light and full of flavor!Broadway Burger Bar & Grill located inside the Village Streets is not only the best tasting burger, but is one of the healthiest burgers you will ever try! Description: Shake Shack is a critically acclaimed, modern day "roadside" burger stand known for its 100% all-natural Angus beef burgers, griddled-crisp flat-top dogs, fresh-made frozen custard, crinkle cut fries, craft beer, wine, and more. Born in NYC's Madison Square Park in 2004 and part of Danny Meyer's Union Square Hospitality Group, Shake Shack has earned a cult-like following around the world with it's fun, lively, and fine-casual widespread appeal.
Location: 3792 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Stroll through the brownstone and tree-lined Greenwich Village and experience sidewalk dining and all its charm. The Village Eateries offer Sirrico_s New York pizza, famous neighborhood sandwiches at Greenberg's Deli, fish, chips, and more at Fulton_s Fish Frye, fresh baked pastries at the Village Bakery and the best hot dogs on the strip at Times Square to Go.
Location: 3792 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
